      <div type="description" n="monument">
        <head>Description of Monument</head>
        <p>Fragment from a <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">balustrade</rs>, broken in two,
with a cross in relief on one side (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.36</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.31</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.155</measure>); the upper edge has a boss protruding
from it, and a polished surface, on which are several finely cut
graffiti.</p></div><div type="description" n="text"><head>Description of text</head><p>i at upper edge; ii below i; iii
along lower edge. There are further traces of letters.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="letters">
        <head>Description of Letters</head>
        <p>Av. <measure precision="circa" type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.005</measure>.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="date">
        <head>Date</head>
        <p><date notAfter="0600" exact="none" notBefore="0401">Fifth to sixth centuries</date> or later (<rs type="criteria">content</rs>, <rs type="criteria">location</rs>).</p>
      </div>

