      <div type="translation">
        <head>Translation</head>
        <ab>i. Theophylaktos.</ab>
        <ab> ii. Georgios. son of Georgios. Lord help. Georgios.</ab>
        <ab>iii. Joannes. Mother of God. Michael <seg cert="low">son of</seg> Palmas.
<seg cert="low">Konstantinos</seg> ... Michael.</ab>
      </div>

      <div type="commentary">
        <head>Commentary</head>
        <p>See discussion at <xref type="eAla-text" n="VIII.13">VIII.13</xref>.</p>
      </div>

